    <div id="toDoBox">
      <h3 class="boxTitle"><img src="/images/boxTitle/toDoIcon.png" class="boxTitleIcon"> To Do</h3>
      <div class="boxContent">
        <%= render :partial => "profiles/todolist" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="travelBox">
      <h3 class="boxTitle"><img src="/images/boxTitle/travelIcon.png" class="boxTitleIcon"> Travel Information</h3>
      <div class="boxContent">
        <ul id="travelList">
          <li><span style="color:grey;">Itinerary</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="smallDescriptionText">Itinerary will become blue when available.
          <% if @profile.project.itinerary_available %>
            You will not receive itinerary info before <%= @profile.project.itinerary_available %>
          <% end %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="centerColumn">
    <div id="supportBox">
      <h3 class="boxTitle"><img src="/images/boxTitle/supportIcon.png" class="boxTitleIcon"> Support</h3>
      <div class="boxContent">
        <h2>You need to raise <%= format_currency(@profile.cached_costing_total) %><% if @profile.project.support_deadline %>by <%= @profile.project.support_deadline %><% end %></h2>
        <p>Your support coach <b><%= @profile.support_coach.name %></b> is here to help you do that.</p>
        <p><b><%= @profile.support_coach.name %></b> •
        <% if cell = @profile.support_coach.person.cell_phone %>
        <b>cell</b>: <%= cell %>
        <% elsif local_phone = @profile.support_coach.person.local_phone %>
        <b>phone</b>: <%= local_phone %>
        <% end %> •
        <b><%= @profile.support_coach.email %></b> </p>
        <h3 id="youveRaisedTitle">You've raised $<span style="color:green;"><%= in_place_editor_field(:profile, :support_claimed_currency) %></span> <span style="color:grey;">We've received $2,500.</span></h3>
        <div id="chartContainer">
          <dl id="chart">
            <dd><span id="data-one" style="width: <%= [@profile.support_claimed_percent, 100].min %>%"><%= @profile.support_claimed_percent %>%</span></dd>
          </dl>
        </div>
        <div id="chartNumbers">
          <table id="chartNumbers">
            <tbody><tr>
                <td style="text-align:left;">$0</td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= format_currency(@profile.cached_costing_total / 2) %></td>
                <td style="text-align:right;"><%= format_currency(@profile.cached_costing_total) %></td>
              </tr>
          </tbody></table>
        </div>
        <h3 class="supportTitles">Expenses</h3>
        <p>You can add some costs, such as vaccinations and medical expenses, to your fundraising amount. Check your acceptance package, or check with your support coach to be sure your expense is covered. <a href="#">Edit expenses.</a></p>
        <h3 class="supportTitles">How to Receive Donations</h3>
        <div id="supportBoxLeftColumn">
          <h4>Online</h4>
          <p>Send this info &amp; donate url to supporters: <a href="#"><%= link_to_function "Click to copy", "prompt('Send this url', 'https://powertochange.com/organization/staff/andrew-roth/')" %></a></p>
        </div>
        <div id="supportBoxRightColumn">
          <h4>Snail Mail</h4>
          <p>Make cheques payable to:<br>
          Power to Change Ministries<br>
          20385 - 64th Avenue<br>
          Langley, BC V2Y 1N5</p>
        </div>
        <h3 class="supportTitles">Tax Receipts for Cash/Cheque Donors</h3>
        <p>For donors giving by cheque to receive a tax receipt, you must fill out the Record of Funds form. Your project number and student ID are <%= @profile.project.cost_center %>-<%= @profile.motivation_code %>. Download it <a href="#">here</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
